description = "An elderly priest of Chronos with a flowing grey beard and robes that have seen better days. Father Aldwin tends to the crumbling Temple of Chronos with quiet dignity, offering what spiritual comfort he can to Aberdeen's desperate populace. His hourglass pendant is tarnished but polished daily, and he speaks of time's passage with a philosopher's acceptance. He believes Chronos tests Aberdeen's faith, and that those who endure will see prosperity again."
